Data Structures Overview

When writing a program, there is a wide variety of commonly used data structures and algorithms available. Having taken an introductory course to the subject, me and a friend decided to write a summary of it.

The document is only available in Swedish and serves as a brief introduction to data structures. More specifically, it tries to concisely summarize the important points of the Chalmer’s course DAT037 Datastrukturer as presented in 2016 and 2017. In 2018, it was recommended as complimentary literature for the course.

The document is available with hyperlinks or for printing.
